# Dashboard

## Layout (v1)

1. `ApprovalCard` banner (when pending; re-highlight on `action_pending_reminder`)
2. `ServerGrid` (Phase 4: CPU/mem sparklines)
3. `IncidentFeed`

Handoff: header button → drawer on `handoff_ready`.

## WebSocket

- `ws.js` singleton only — no REST polling for live state.
- HIGH risk: type `CONFIRM` before approve.
- Sensitive service: amber banner; risk bump per DECISIONS.md.

## Build

`npm run build` → `dashboard/dist/` served by FastAPI.
